{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5f27be6d0f","title":"在一份外交信稿上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"131c641295","index":0,"year":1962,"month":11,"day":27,"articleId":"5f27be6d0f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"84bed7930f","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指外交部起草的中华人民共和国国务院总理周恩来1962年11月27日给细甸联邦革命政府部长会议主席奈温的信稿。"},{"id":"fadaf64e37","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东在审阅这份信稿时，将“阁下对和平解决中印边界问题所持的公正态度.....对巩固亚非国家的团结、维护亚洲的和平，也将是珍贵的责献”一句中的“珍贵的”改为“有益的”；将“中印边境上原先十分险恶的局势已经开始有了好转机”一句中的“原先十分险恶的局势”改为“原先的那种局势”，将“转机”改为“缓和”；对“仅仅中国一方面采取这种行动，还不能完全有效地防止冲突不再起，也不利于为谈判创造良好的气氛”一句，删去“完全有效地”，将“防止冲突不再起”改为“防止冲突的再起”，删去“也不利于”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"30ab60b26e","type":"title","text":"在一份外交信稿叫上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f"},{"id":"84bed7930f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f"},{"id":"fadaf64e37","type":"paragraph","text":"近几天一些外交文件，在措词方面有些欠当，这就是一件，我改了一点，请你再阅。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f"},{"id":"142e47026d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f"},{"id":"2210992811","type":"paragraph","text":"廿七日早","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f"}],"page":{"id":"84053c4647","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"5f27be6d0f","start":299,"end":299}}}},"__N_SSG":true}